<div class="fr-view Kanit panel-content-htmleditor"><div class="fr-view Kanit panel-content-htmleditor"><p><strong><em>How to Choose the Right Material for Comfort and Style</em></strong></p><p><span style="font-family: Georgia,serif;">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style="font-family: Georgia,serif;">When producing uniforms or fashion apparel, the first thing to consider isn&rsquo;t just the design&mdash;it&rsquo;s the &quot;fabric.&quot;&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style="font-family: Georgia,serif;">Each material has unique properties. Choosing the right one enhances your corporate image and ensures wearer confidence all day long.</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style="font-family: Georgia,serif;"><strong>1. Fabrics for Uniforms and Polo Shirts</strong></span></p><p><span style="font-family: Georgia,serif;">CVC Fabric (80% Cotton + 20% Poly): Smooth, highly breathable, and excellent at absorbing sweat. It holds its shape well, making it perfect for premium office uniforms.</span></p><p><span style="font-family: Georgia,serif;">TC Fabric (35% Cotton + 65% Poly): The most popular choice for polos. It&rsquo;s wrinkle-resistant, easy to iron, and budget-friendly.</span></p><p><span style="font-family: Georgia,serif;">TK Fabric (100% Polyester): Features vibrant colors that won&rsquo;t fade. It&rsquo;s the most economical option, ideal for short-term events or promotional giveaways.</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style="font-family: Georgia,serif;"><strong>2. Fabrics for T-shirts and Fashion</strong></span></p><p><span style="font-family: Georgia,serif;">100% Cotton: Offers a natural feel and superior breathability. Available in various weights (e.g., No.20, No.32), it&rsquo;s the top choice for clothing brands.</span></p><p><span style="font-family: Georgia,serif;">Supersoft Fabric: Cotton that has been brushed for a velvet-like finish, providing a luxurious and high-end feel.</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style="font-family: Georgia,serif;"><strong>3. Fabrics for Premiums and Bags</strong></span></p><p><span style="font-family: Georgia,serif;">Canvas: Thick, durable, and naturally stylish. Perfect for premium eco-friendly tote bags.</span></p><p><span style="font-family: Georgia,serif;">600D Fabric: A synthetic material that is water-resistant and sturdy. Ideal for backpacks or laptop bags.</span></p><p><br></p><p>😊😊😊😊😊😊😊😊😊😊😊😊😊😊😊😊😊😊😊😊😊😊😊😊😊😊😊😊😊😊😊😊😊😊😊😊😊😊</p><p data-f-id="pbf" style="text-align: center; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px; opacity: 0.65; font-family: sans-serif;">Powered by <a href="https://www.froala.com/wysiwyg-editor?pb=1" title="Froala Editor">Froala Editor</a></p></div></div><p data-f-id="pbf" style="text-align: center; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px; opacity: 0.65; font-family: sans-serif;">Powered by <a href="https://www.froala.com/wysiwyg-editor?pb=1" title="Froala Editor">Froala Editor</a></p><p data-f-id="pbf" style="text-align: center; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px; opacity: 0.65; font-family: sans-serif;">Powered by <a href="https://www.froala.com/wysiwyg-editor?pb=1" title="Froala Editor">Froala Editor</a></p><p data-f-id="pbf" style="text-align: center; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px; opacity: 0.65; font-family: sans-serif;">Powered by <a href="https://www.froala.com/wysiwyg-editor?pb=1" title="Froala Editor">Froala Editor</a></p><p data-f-id="pbf" style="text-align: center; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px; opacity: 0.65; font-family: sans-serif;">Powered by <a href="https://www.froala.com/wysiwyg-editor?pb=1" title="Froala Editor">Froala Editor</a></p>